{
    "version": "1.1.3",
    "description": "CMS Detection and Exploitation suite - Scan WordPress, Joomla, Drupal and over 180 other CMSs.",
    "homepage": "https://github.com/Tuhinshubhra/CMSeeK",
    "license": "GPL-3.0",
    "suggest": {
        "python": "uv"
    },
    "url": "https://github.com/Tuhinshubhra/CMSeeK/archive/refs/heads/master.zip",
    "extract_dir": "CMSeeK-master",
    "pre_install": [
        "Set-Content \"$dir\\CMSeeK.bat\" '@pushd %~dp0",
        "@uv run python \"cmseek.py\" %*",
        "@popd' -Encoding Ascii"
    ],
    "post_install": [
        "uv venv \"$dir\\.venv\"",
        "uv pip install -r $dir\\requirements.txt --python \"$dir\\.venv\\Scripts\\python.exe\""
    ],
    "bin": "CMSeeK.bat",
    "notes": [
        "【工具类型】: Python工具",
        "【主要功能】: CMS Detection and Exploitation suite - Scan WordPress, Joomla, Drupal and over 180 other CMSs.",
        "【适用场景】: 根据描述推断的适用场景",
        "【技术特点】: 基于Python开发，需Python环境"
    ]
}
